modShortDescription: Just a craftable chess table and chess pieces, using red, blue and classic notation for the pieces. The set is crafted as a bundle that includes the table.
modDescription:
Just a craftable chess table and chess pieces, using red, blue and classic notation for the pieces. The set is crafted as a bundle that includes the table. Gathering all the pieces again lets you craft a bundle without the table.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Snufki-n/Snufkin_Modlets/tree/master/Snufkin_Chess)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/18673-snufkins-assorted-modlets/).
